title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 22 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 22 2022
description:
Senator Marco Rubio joins Clay and Buck the day after his debate drubbing of Val Demings. Gen-X voters are most anti-Biden generation. 25-year-old former Trump staffer Karoline Leavitt joins C&B to explain why Granite-Staters (that's New Hampshire) are about to send her to Congress. Ben Domenech thinks the GOP could win 40 House seats.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
